  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.6">
<l>palapalavē yāparaṇam pērumpala palavē</l>
<l>palapalavē cōti vaṭivupaṇ peṇṇil</l>
<l>palapala kaṇṭuṇṭu kēṭṭuṟṟu mōntiṉpam</l>
<l>palapalavē ñāṉamum pāmpaṇaimē lāṟkēyō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Manny many the ornaments, the names many many,</l>
<l>many many the luminous forms if one counts the qualities,</l>
<l>many many the pleasures of seeing, absorbing, hearing, experiencing, smelling,</l>
<l>many many the knowledges of him on the serpent bed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
